2. Iterate through the prices vector and convert each word to a double using std::stod().
3. Calculate the discounted price by multiplying the price by (1 - (double)discount / 100.0).
4. Round the discounted price to two decimal places using std::fixed and std::setprecision(2).
5. Append the discounted price to the result string.
6. Return the result string.

